msgid ""
"Describe a time by reference to the current day, like '+90 days' (90 "
"days from the day the field is created) or '+1 Saturday' (the next "
"Saturday). See <a "
"href=\"http://php.net/manual/function.strtotime.php\">strtotime</a> "
